data.title: CONSTRUCCIONES AERONAUTICAS, S.A. (CASA) Model CN-235 series airplanes
data.meta_description: CONSTRUCCIONES AERONAUTICAS, S.A. (CASA) Model CN-235 series airplanes (Docket No. 96-NM-137-AD) - proposes to require repetitive inspections of the torsion tubes and fittings of the elevator and rudder assemblies to detect stress corrosion cracking, and replacement of cracked parts. The proposed AD also would require a modification that would constitute terminating action for the repetitive inspections.
